5.94{\\pm}0.49)\\,$% and\n$QF_W^{ROI}=(1.72{\\pm}0.21)\\,$%. The latest CRESST data (run32) is reanalyzed\nusing these fundamentally new results on light quenching in CaWO$_4$ having\nmoderate influence on the WIMP analysis. Their relevance for future CRESST runs\nand for the clarification of previously published results of direct Dark Matter\nexperiments is emphasized.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 14 Jan 2014 18:20:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Jan 2016 14:04:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-01-26"}
