ults were again obtained in the evaluation\n(F-measure 40.36% for QA plus Spanish temporal layer vs. 22.94% for the general\nQA system).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 2014 05:35:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-16"}
