ity and innovation orientation to prevent societal lock-ins\nsuch as the ones we are experiencing in assisting our elderly ones.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jan 2014 15:06:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-01-16"}
